Publisher's Description+


                From  Alexander Sludnikov: 


    MyMedia allows you to freely download videos, songs, images and documents right to your device, like in a real browser!MyMedia is absolutely free and allows you to download without any limits. View your files anywhere and anytime. MyMedia is compatible with the iPhone, iPad and iPod Touch.FEATURESWeb Browser- Great browsing experience which enables you to find the files you need easily.- Tabbed browsing, full screen mode, bookmarks, history management and much more!- Download files just by holding your finger on a link. Alternatively, if you want to download from a specific url, just type it in the address bar and the download will begin.Download Manager- All the files are downloaded simultaneously and there is no limitation on the number of files that can be downloaded. - Supports background downloads.- Resumable downloads. File Manager- Manage your downloads by creating folders. You can move your files between folders, rename or delete them. - Open files you downloaded in MyMedia in other apps. This will enable you, for example, to open a video you downloaded in a video editing app or a document in a document reader.- Open files from other apps in MyMedia. For example you can extract the contents of a zip or rar file of other apps with MyMedia.- View the images you download in a special album. You can easily edit and export them.- Handles zip/rar filesPlay Videos- Play all video format that are support by your iPhone.- Save videos to your camera roll.- View videos in external display- AirPlay supportListen to Music- Play all audio formats that are supports by your iPhone.- Play your tracks in a playlist.- The Music player presents the album artwork that is played- Ability to play music sequentially in the background.- AirPlay supportExport your Files- Supports iTunes USB file sharing- Supports AirDrop- Transfer files using your WIFI network (HTTP File Sharing)- Upload your files to dropbox- Send your files via Email.Security- Enable private browsing - Enable passcode lock.

            

